{"tid":2388514,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"旺角街站介紹「武裝起義」歷史，警員警告或違反國安法！","createTime":"2021-01-31T07:58:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T08:31:35.000Z","uid":219007,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b5815dcc9d591d9b82ef04b898fb78c675bc0471","tid":2388514,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:58:10.000Z","msg":"【組織介紹「武裝起義」歷史　遭發限聚令告票】<br />\n<br />\n組織「光城者」下午約 1 時在旺角站 E 出口雅蘭中心處擺設街站，向市民介紹各地「武裝起義」歷史。<br />\n<br />\n近 30 名警員在近 3 時到場，包圍 5 名成員，並拉起橙帶設封鎖區。<br />\n<br />\n成員被查問約 30 分鐘，期間記者被攔在封鎖區外，未能了解查問詳情，有成員引述警員曾指他們有機會違反國安法。警員最終向成員發限聚令告票後離去，有成員表明不會繳交罰款。<br />\n<br />\n直播重溫：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2NLWifT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2NLWifT&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWgESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=fa7510aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2NLWifT</a>"},{"pid":"c99cddef8d1202e66b1b5ce244490559ef30303b","tid":2388514,"uid":51271,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:59:07.000Z","msg":"咁講文革囉"},{"pid":"a548c9676d8b4f62ccf73a1cf0b60ff53c0d4a7b","tid":2388514,"uid":6604,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:59:34.000Z","msg":"共產黨當年咪又係武裝起義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0af764d1ebdc9e94fea06feae0fd9b1c1c29b62d","tid":2388514,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a548c9676d8b4f62ccf73a1cf0b60ff53c0d4a7b","tid":2388514,"uid":6604,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:59:34.000Z","msg":"共產黨當年咪又係武裝起義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:01:50.000Z","msg":"老毛紅軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25a0838797514c4224ed1e2839c1f39c778298d1","tid":2388514,"uid":15880,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a548c9676d8b4f62ccf73a1cf0b60ff53c0d4a7b","tid":2388514,"uid":6604,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy"